        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nHi,\n\nThis commit aims to refactor CsarUtil::extractVfcArtifact. Some other functions had to be modified slightly in order to prevent returning nulls (which is a bad practice in general as it forces the caller to think about adding a null check, which if omitted will potentially throw a null pointer exception).\n\nThank you in advance for your help.\n\nFrancis.",
